name: Little hope
description:
In a world of appearances where everyone wants to be like the famous, there is a light, a little hope in your journey that makes you realize that this is not the way to go. Even having what the stars have, you realize that's not what would make you happy, that realization makes you stand out from the crowd and follow your own path. The stars end up dying sooner or later, the flower that has been shining for too long is not real and is dead inside, only evil forces are holding them while they benefit.

Resolution: 960x958
Tools used: GLIDE, image editor, SwinIR, C-aLDI, AIVA, video editor

More info in the webpage ^^
